# NOTE: The following are NOT ignored (committed for backup continuity):
# - db/custom.db         (enriched skill data)
# - scripts/lurker.state.json  (lurker progress)
# - scripts/lurker.lock        (PID lock)
# - worklog.md          (agent work log)
# - CHANGELOG.md        (versioned changelog)
# - docs/               (project documentation + chat history)
# - tool-results/       (temporary tool outputs — can be ignored)
tool-results/